%% 3.2.1 Edit Student Profile — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (Student Detail)
    participant SC as Controller (StudentController)
    participant SS as Service (StudentService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository Student)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    UI->>SC: GET /api/Student/Get/{id} — load detail
    SC-->>UI: StudentDto

    Actor->>UI: Edit → change FullName, CampusId, ...
    alt Required field empty (FE)
        UI-->>Actor: Inline error — block request
    else Valid
        UI->>SC: PUT /api/Student/Update/{id} StudentUpdateDto
        SC->>SS: UpdateStudentAsync
        SS->>SS: ValidateCampus, dedupe rules
        SS->>Repo: Update + SaveChanges
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE Students
        SS-->>SC: StudentDto
        SC-->>UI: 200
        UI-->>Actor: Toast — profile updated, read-only mode
    end
